Dwarf Planet: Pluto

Distance from Sun: 39.5AU
Size:2,377km (Dwarf Planet)
Gravity: 0.062g (0.62m/s^2)

Further details:
While not technically a planet Pluto is often considered worthy enough to be of note. Its primary export is Ice which is mined from the surface and shipped out to Bars and research stations across the sector.
